パッケージ ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities

クラス ClassHistory

java.lang.Object
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.AbstractHistory
ch.uzh.ifi.seal.changedistiller.model.entities.ClassHistory
public class ClassHistory
extends AbstractHistory
Class histories store change data about the history of a class. It contains its attribute, inner classe, and method histories. Top most element for histories.

Label: 

 ClassHistory:<className>

Unique name: 

 qualified class name
作成者:
Beat Fluri, zubi, Giacomo Ghezzi
関連項目:
AbstractHistory, AttributeHistory, MethodHistory

    • createInnerClassHistory

      public ClassHistory createInnerClassHistory​(StructureEntityVersion clazz)
      Create an inner class history for the unique name of the given class version if it does not exist. The history is attached to the class history of this history.
      パラメータ:
      clazz - the class version for which a history is to be created
      戻り値:
      class history for the given class version

    • deleteMethod

      public void deleteMethod​(StructureEntityVersion method)
      Deletes the provided StructureEntityVersion from the corresponding MethodHistory.

      If the corresponding history has not any versions left, it is also deleted.

      パラメータ:
      method - the structure entity version to delete from the corresponding method history
